<br>
I AWLAYS will do whatever is in my means to help an honest-to-Karana roleplaying character.  Even a beggar.  if they cna take the time to play in character and create a story, its worth a few plat.<br>
<br>
I know that this game is not essentially a roleplaying game, not in the sense I am most familiar with, but it's a close approximation.  And roleplaying can be infused, if people take the time.  Its fun to create tales inside of the framework and it adds to the texture and variety of gameplay.<br>
<br>
I'd like to have my guild become a RPG guild, but that's just not practical.  The concept of roleplaying varies betwene people and enforcing that is unfair at best, disasterous at worst.<br>
<br>
